155	4. MODELO DE NEGOCIO\nConsignado? Nao trabalhamos com consignado. Focamos no modelo de ATACADO para garantir margens de lucro muito maiores para voce.\nComo funciona consignado? No consignado voce ganharia apenas 30%. No nosso atacado, voce ganha 100% ou mais.\nDevolver pecas? Oferecemos a primeira troca gratis para pecas que nao girarem em 30 dias.\nPrazo troca: Ate 30 dias apos a compra para manter seu mostruario sempre novo.\nVenda no Atacado: Sim, este e o nosso modelo principal.\nMinimo Atacado: R$ 300 acumulados no pedido.\nDesconto progressivo: Sim, para pedidos acima de R$ 2.000 oferecemos condicoes diferenciadas.\nMisturar pecas: Sim, voce pode escolher 1 peca de cada modelo se desejar.\nMultimarcas: Voce tem liberdade total para vender outros produtos se quiser.\nExclusividade: Nao exigimos exclusividade, mas nossas pecas costumam ser as favoritas das clientes.	[0.0044585494,0.042487353,0.0041372715,0.01660154,0.018057125,-0.004006138,-0.022909077,0.026423462,-0.010116973,-0.044611722,0.034147244,-0.0062255776,-0.0061206706,-0.023840126,0.009684232,-0.0025489135,0.012379032,-0.03928769,-0.019722525,0.027144698,-0.004091375,0.040389214,-0.0058157844,-0.033229306,0.007500854,-0.0027292224,-0.033570256,-0.022882849,0.038920514,-0.062996686,0.016378613,-0.013113381,-0.0018162032,0.0019211103,-0.057436608,0.028928118,0.010687405,0.0055797435,0.011290621,0.014450946,-0.010648065,0.07175642,-0.00066591386,0.0018129249,0.052925605,0.049122725,-0.01609012,0.004150385,-0.013264185,0.025767794,-0.0042913537,0.04899159,0.012333135,0.018607888,0.005583022,-0.039156556,-0.0074877404,-0.0480212,0.02167642,0.0026292328,-0.0046781986,-0.029111706,-0.0013932968,0.011749589,-0.043379065,0.025964495,-0.041674323,0.02365654,-0.07563798,-0.002527604,-0.025387505,-0.0040520346,0.007671328,-0.04747044,-0.0049798065,-0.036638785,-0.012516722,0.0049994765,0.020011019,0.02490231,-0.05549583,0.006858298,0.009507202,0.030921353,-0.011461095,-0.025728453,-0.05229616,5.7422265e-05,-