138	1. PERGUNTAS INICIAIS / INTERESSE\nComo comeco? Voce inicia preenchendo nosso formulario de qualificacao. Apos a aprovacao, agendamos uma reuniao para apresentar o catalogo e as condicoes.\nQuero ser revendedora: Excelente! O primeiro passo e o cadastro que a Amanda envia por aqui mesmo.\nPreciso de experiencia? Nao, nos fornecemos treinamento completo e suporte para quem esta comecando do zero.\nSem loja fisica? Sim! 90% das nossas revendedoras vendem pelo WhatsApp e Instagram.\nZero conhecimento? Sim, ensinamos tudo sobre banhos, pedrarias e tecnicas de venda.\nCidades/Estados: Atendemos todo o Brasil via envio express.\nPreciso de CNPJ? Nao, voce pode revender como pessoa fisica (CPF).\nMenor de idade: Apenas com autorizacao e acompanhamento dos responsaveis legais.\nComo me cadastro? Basta pedir o link do formulario para a Amanda e preencher os dados.\nO que preciso? Vontade de empreender, um smartphone com internet e o investimento inicial para o seu primeiro mostruario.	[0.0021309063,0.070012994,0.030376378,0.05485988,-0.011645447,-0.005778878,0.008447627,0.013972199,-0.00872824,0.028786236,0.02036784,-0.017105712,-0.011394065,-0.046628557,0.030797297,0.045552876,0.009324542,-0.014825731,-0.014346349,0.014580194,0.04052522,0.037578784,-0.04985561,-0.059677072,-0.006120875,-0.04045507,-0.0037181247,-0.013375895,-0.029791767,-0.029300693,-0.012089752,-0.018321702,-0.032574516,0.023933968,-0.004174121,0.07903938,0.0009843385,-0.018976467,0.014556809,0.018918006,-0.016848484,0.012358673,0.01921031,0.02595672,0.003358589,0.038864926,-0.06795516,0.013387588,0.017982628,-0.01831001,0.015726032,0.04031476,0.02394566,0.012580825,-0.05060391,-0.040852603,-0.0015579878,-0.047026094,-0.04485134,0.013703277,0.01461527,0.010254074,0.022811513,-0.0022449056,-0.0375554,0.020543223,-0.011996214,-0.008529472,-0.046464868,0.024974573,-0.03591849,-0.008494395,0.025395494,-0.0142645035,-0.037976317,-0.012171597,-0.015807876,0.02051984,-0.042933818,-0.0014593347,-0.0659441,-0.0