144	2. INVESTIMENTO E CUSTOS\nQuanto investir? Sugerimos um investimento inicial entre R$ 300 e R$ 1.000 para um mostruario competitivo.\nPedido minimo: R$ 300 para garantir o preco de atacado.\nKit inicial: Oferecemos kits prontos ou voce pode montar seu proprio mix de pecas.\nTaxa de cadastro: Nao cobramos taxa de cadastro. O investimento e 100% convertido em produtos.\nGratis cadastrar? Sim, o cadastro e gratuito.\nInvestimento ideal: R$ 500 e o valor mais comum entre nossas novas revendedoras de sucesso.\nPouco dinheiro: Sim, o setor de semijoias e o melhor para comecar com pouco.\nR$300? Sim! Com R$300 voce ja inicia com uma selecao basica de brincos e colares.\nMensalidade? Nao existe nenhuma taxa mensal.\nPagar todo mes? Voce so paga quando quiser repor seu estoque.\nFormas de pagamento: PIX, Cartao de Credito (ate 12x) e Boleto Bancario (a vista).\nParcelam? Sim, em ate [X] vezes no cartao.\nAceitam PIX? Sim, com liberacao imediata do pedido.	[-0.0014406963,0.03412275,0.0084171975,0.0017086596,-0.00052489265,0.011708416,0.030718042,0.028599557,0.0043788343,-0.03424885,0.034854133,-0.024993086,-0.00063050166,-0.06330237,0.023227682,0.019545551,-0.005469602,-0.009905182,-0.035862934,0.024551736,0.021033537,0.051045418,-0.0603264,-0.031045903,0.028372576,-0.014085407,-0.0077614756,-0.0146654695,0.01865024,-0.065067776,0.010731138,-0.0058447504,-0.030945022,0.028145595,-0.05977156,0.047489386,-0.025295727,-0.0046846275,0.038939785,0.017981907,-0.027464652,0.04892693,0.017843198,-0.013089214,0.011475131,0.014413268,-0.03709872,-0.0115318755,0.005983461,0.014766349,-0.017414456,0.039040662,-0.013845817,0.017805368,-0.019394232,-0.038586702,-0.020087784,-0.02278633,-0.025358777,0.019734703,0.036165576,-0.015976913,0.025901008,-0.009217935,-0.0222441,0.05245774,-0.026758492,0.014703299,-0.050742775,0.029154398,-0.029078737,-0.032458227,0.04819555,-0.036165576,-0.020251714,-0.022117998,-0.04022601,0.0062419665,0.021739697,0.0143249985,-0.047968566,-0.01480418,0.00639