150	3. LUCRO E GANHOS\nMargem de lucro? Nossa margem recomendada e de 100% a 300%.\nGanho por peca? Se voce compra por R$ 30, vende por R$ 60 a R$ 90.\nLucro medio? A maioria das revendedoras atinge 150% de lucro real.\nDobrar valor? Com certeza! E o padrao do mercado de semijoias premium.\nPorcentagem: De 100% (minimo) ate 300% em pecas exclusivas.\nGanhos mensais: Revendedoras iniciantes ganham de R$ 800 a R$ 2.000. Profissionais passam de R$ 5.000.\nViver de revenda? Sim, temos parceiras que fizeram disso sua unica e principal renda.\nGanhar R$2.000? Totalmente possivel com uma carteira de 20 a 30 clientes ativas.\nCalcular preco: Ensinamos uma formula simples: (Custo + Despesas + Margem de Lucro).\nPreco sugerido: Sim, enviamos uma tabela com sugestoes, mas voce tem liberdade total.\nIndicacao: Sim, temos um programa de bonus por indicacao de novas parceiras.\nGanho por indicacao: Voce ganha [X]% sobre o primeiro pedido da indicacao.	[0.017187499,0.028952396,0.009823987,0.014177596,-0.009704547,0.007303791,0.019731583,0.030648451,0.032631166,-0.0387943,0.032917824,0.0025754375,-0.026850242,-0.045530748,0.043763027,0.0075486447,0.008516113,-0.01636336,-0.036620483,0.02546473,0.03181897,0.049639504,-0.031126214,-0.012624869,0.033801682,-0.008402645,0.0061004274,0.0059182807,0.038316537,-0.04715514,0.015360058,-0.006013833,0.020400451,0.0014131314,-0.05651928,0.035449963,-0.013520674,-0.0031771194,0.03523497,0.027447445,-0.021511247,0.0854239,0.0023275982,0.0039923014,0.029191278,0.01939715,0.0107735405,-0.005995917,0.044169124,0.037289347,-0.020997653,0.043165825,0.019409094,0.06402015,-0.057092596,-0.03561718,-0.023063976,-0.010761596,-0.031890634,0.0063303504,0.020125737,-0.019994352,0.028283529,-0.01813108,-0.023792563,0.025249738,-0.03384946,-0.0009779198,-0.023338689,0.016208086,-0.004493952,0.00575405,0.0466296,-0.012397932,-0.02599027,-0.018369962,0.017784702,0.02016157,-0.0033861403,0.023649234,-0.012672645,-0.039821487,0.0020170528,0.05513377,-0.04464689,