160	5. PRODUTOS E QUALIDADE\nBanhadas a ouro? Sim, banho de ouro 18k de alta qualidade.\nMilesimos: Nossas pecas tem entre 7 a 10 milesimos de ouro (padrao luxo).\nEscurecem? Semijoias de qualidade nao escurecem se cuidadas corretamente.\nDuracao do banho: Com uso correto, o banho dura anos.\nSemijoia vs Bijuteria: Bijuteria e apenas pintada. Semijoia recebe camadas reais de ouro e metais nobres.\nHipoalergicas? Sim, todas as nossas pecas sao NIQUEL-FREE (nao causam alergia).\nMaterial base: Latao de alta fusao.\nPedras Naturais: Usamos Zirconias premium e, em algumas linhas, pedras naturais brasileiras.\nPrata: Temos a linha Prata 925 legitima.\nRodio: Oferecemos pecas no banho de Rodio Branco (cor prata) e Rodio Negro.\nGarantia: 1 ano no banho e contra defeitos de fabricacao.\nCobre o que? Perda de banho e defeitos estruturais. Nao cobre quebra ou mau uso.\nRebanho: Oferecemos servico de rebanho para pecas antigas com custo reduzido.\nLancamentos: Temos novidades toda semana.	[0.032332048,0.053323753,-0.0054590493,0.015369788,-0.0018639185,-0.020316109,-0.015719648,0.02075042,0.016720977,-0.086813964,0.027409857,-0.01213055,-0.060514014,-0.047436424,0.044203218,0.051731277,-0.021257116,-0.028206093,-0.005627948,0.0031578036,0.014489101,0.01690194,-0.033948652,-0.0031578036,0.05409586,-0.033031773,-0.009204983,0.007883953,0.04492707,-0.0053957123,0.06635308,-0.0074677384,0.03170471,0.023585506,-0.026348207,0.015285338,0.04873936,-0.034913786,0.04567505,0.007497899,0.018892532,0.037326626,-0.032066636,-0.0010066065,0.03457599,0.050235316,0.004521058,-0.024731604,-0.0055404827,0.04883587,0.022318766,0.05066963,-0.014730385,0.005437937,0.0017176401,-0.0444445,0.0005300707,-0.016310794,-0.06403676,-0.03414168,0.011159383,-0.043213956,-0.021450143,0.013101718,-0.04975275,0.0025470536,-0.04914954,-0.02388711,-0.020545328,-0.0040716664,0.021196796,-9.213089e-06,0.027144443,0.008354457,-0.053275496,-0.01359635,0.003172884,-0.0015351691,0.034045164,0.025793254,-0.04207992,