166	6. ENTREGA E LOGISTICA\nComo entrega? Via Correios (SEDEX/PAC) ou Transportadora parceira.\nBrasil todo? Sim, chegamos em qualquer CEP do Brasil.\nPrazo: De 2 a 7 dias uteis apos o despacho, dependendo da regiao.\nFrete Gratis: Sim, para pedidos acima de R$ [X].\nCusto Frete: Calculado pelo CEP, geralmente entre R$ 20 e R$ 40 para capitais.\nDiscreta: Sim, enviamos em caixas seguras sem identificacao externa.\nEmbalagem presente: Vendemos kits de presente separadamente com preco de custo.	[0.025584366,0.033199556,0.032798756,0.023914369,0.00999772,0.009674854,0.0034819455,0.0250945,-0.018492442,-0.028790763,-0.0064016585,0.023847569,-0.011033119,-0.044755943,0.025673432,0.03649502,0.018815309,-0.011489585,-0.041237812,0.007487157,0.018926643,0.030037694,-0.009240654,-0.03622782,0.015586646,-0.016020846,-0.013259782,0.009953187,0.023290902,-0.023958903,0.0045646606,-0.004670427,0.016087646,0.005883959,-0.024159301,0.04747247,-0.043553542,0.003259279,0.0057893256,0.014373114,-0.019371975,0.035203554,0.0050099934,-0.014695981,0.008951188,0.018548109,-0.027053965,-0.019193841,-0.0041026277,0.042863276,0.032665156,0.05887299,0.0004926494,0.033288624,0.033533555,-0.024292901,-0.010465319,-0.014751648,0.018837575,0.00799929,0.006323725,0.00504896,-0.031707693,0.03484729,0.007977023,0.01539738,-0.059318323,-0.0054915096,-0.040480748,0.008505856,-0.049521003,0.027855564,0.023068236,-0.051079668,0.008210823,0.0107770525,0.010092353,-0.016588645,0.036005154,7.154027e-05,-0.08211936,-0.006067659,0.0020819306,0.029881828,-0.07530577,-0.048986603,-0.04428834,0.023892103,-0.036873553,0.0095189875,-0.045869272,-0.012480451,-0.01003112,0.056601793,-0.016098779,0.0019497224,-0.03137369,-0.03987955,0.022322305,0.027632898,0.056868993,-0.05522126,0.015920646,-0.018915508,0.013560383,-0.030371694,-0.04618101,0.011701118,0.006975024,-0.034735955,0.044310607,-0.0031841293,-0.022155304,0.084078826,0.020930639,0.03317729,0.03743022,-0.036695417,-0.0040887115,0.008856555,-0.028857563,0.0