181	9. DUVIDAS OPERACIONAIS\nEstoque em casa? Sim, ter o produto a pronta entrega e o segredo da venda rapida.\nControlar estoque: Fornecemos uma planilha simples de entradas e saidas.\nPeca encalhada: Use como brinde em compras grandes ou faca promocao de queima de estoque.\nReceber clientes: Dinheiro, PIX ou Link de Pagamento.\nMaquininha: Sim, hoje em dia e indispensavel ter uma (ex: PagSeguro, Mercado Pago).\nPronta entrega: Sim, enviamos em ate 24h uteis apos o pedido.	[0.0013946157,0.05727182,-0.025553154,-0.00044894134,0.032176264,-0.0132703,-0.019977702,0.035259016,-0.009850368,-0.04484446,0.044386864,-0.030273624,-0.008585956,-0.040870596,0.02762438,-0.017436836,-0.007887519,-0.028467322,-0.016906988,-0.018026896,0.0046000495,0.01895413,-0.029165758,-0.041159604,-0.0056868414,-0.0027245057,-0.02935843,-0.01805098,0.0057470514,-0.028178314,0.010861897,-0.016485518,-0.0011996856,0.009964767,-0.010807708,0.05423723,-0.008676271,-0.01357135,0.035957456,-0.019243138,-0.03718574,0.02439712,-0.0073516495,-0.01853266,0.04359209,0.019700736,-0.04255648,-0.050431956,0.019219054,0.06507505,0.008375221,0.017774014,-0.0069482424,0.022590818,8.043689e-05,-0.030345876,-0.02678144,-0.05847602,0.02462592,0.02702228,0.0054791165,-0.014956182,-0.0055694315,0.0045518815,-0.00062957156,0.033645388,-0.030321792,0.023144752,-0.10385033,-0.0070867254,-0.047445536,0.020290794,0.02385523,-0.04874607,0.022277726,-0.029671524,-0.019471938,0.005421917,0.018508576,0.008086213,-0.04120777,-0.045013048,0.004401356,0.02074839,-0.025456818,-0.051443484,-0.07152957,-0.0033567115,-0.03940147,-0.0076527,-0.03884754,0.028057894,0.019026382,0.0450853,-0.013065586,0.010265817,-0.0020170375,-0.0036788352,-0.02504739,0.033452716,0.055104256,-0.02564949,0.013667686,-0.043254916,0.020411214,-0.0055333055,-0.042821404,0.021145778,0.016365098,-0.0265406,0.019712778,-0.032802448,-0.009597485,0.08887006,0.021482954,-0.0061715324,0.047854964,0.0045277975,0.002462592,0.0018966172,-0.012042014,0.041520864,-