186	10. MEDOS E OBJECOES\nNao vender? Improvavel. O mercado de acessorios e um dos que mais cresce. Nos te daremos o treinamento.\nPerder dinheiro: O investimento em ouro (semijoia) e um ativo. Voce tem o produto fisico em maos.\nGolpe? Verifique nosso CNPJ e redes sociais com depoimentos de revendedoras reais.\nNunca vendi: Todo mundo comeca do zero. A Amanda e nossa equipe vao te guiar.\nMercado saturado? Nunca. Mulheres compram acessorios novos todos os meses.	[0.036928285,0.07828796,0.013663465,0.049152818,-0.0054978575,0.013141375,0.012772093,0.02801456,0.00040828038,-0.04821051,0.044721425,-0.044161133,-0.023035608,-0.061581094,0.02330302,0.03687735,-0.025200369,-0.039220385,0.0047242735,0.028141899,0.028753126,0.07441686,-0.025646055,-0.04169076,0.027148655,-0.029593563,-0.026066273,-0.0014055031,0.009346676,-0.0006665396,0.058219347,-0.028294705,-0.006755329,0.02444907,-0.0023350772,0.06117361,0.012969468,-0.03206394,0.036342524,0.0038010664,0.0022538987,0.044950634,0.016413985,0.023786908,0.025149435,0.018922562,-0.008741816,-0.0026438741,0.010524561,0.034967262,-0.016936075,0.048516124,0.012262736,0.05638567,-0.028269237,-0.054450117,-0.020476095,-0.03165645,-0.016222976,0.020068612,0.00074891193,-0.02199143,0.0047179065,0.020603435,-0.014338361,0.0037946994,-0.023583166,0.005389619,-0.03616425,0.016770534,-0.03338826,-0.014096417,0.040340967,-0.0037214796,-0.01934278,-0.03545115,-0.016210243,-0.024079787,0.013497924,-0.0047051725,-0.047930364,0.004998052,0.0014842942,0.026257282,-0.068915814,-0.009811463,-0.03534928,-0.043880988,-0.024130723,0.008709981,-0.07197195,-0.020170484,0.025607854,0.0243854,-0.0121927,-0.002608856,-0.011409566,-0.016286647,-0.0058162045,0.03007745,0.0035973242,-0.005704783,0.026817573,0.011364997,-7.013588e-05,0.02163488,-0.028778594,-0.06336384,-0.019584725,0.036087845,0.03570583,-0.03743764,0.0026375072,0.021303799,0.02880406,0.042327452,0.025187636,0.014542103,0.038176205,-0.0899522,-0.04477236,0.008098754,0.015420741,-0.02513