191	11. PERGUNTAS ESPECIFICAS DO FLUXO\nPor que formulario? Para conhecermos seu perfil e garantirmos que voce esta pronta para lucrar com a gente.\nSeguranca: Seus dados sao protegidos pela LGPD.\nConsulta CPF: Fazemos uma analise basica, mas ter restricao nao impede necessariamente de revender.\nNome Negativado: Sim, voce pode ser revendedora basta pagar as compras a vista (PIX/Cartao).\nPor que reuniao? Para te mostrar o plano de lucros detalhado e tirar todas as suas duvidas ao vivo.\nTempo reuniao: Aproximadamente 15 a 20 minutos. E rapida e objetiva.\nOnline/Presencial: Geralmente online via video-chamada para sua comodidade.\nReuniao gratuita? Sim, 100% gratuita.\nO que e ser aprovada? Significa que seu perfil bate com o de nossas revendedoras de sucesso.\nReprovada: Apos 3 meses voce pode tentar um novo cadastro.\nTempo aprovacao: Geralmente o sistema valida em poucos minutos apos o formulario.	[0.00740637,0.021293314,0.010333887,0.014374863,-0.0035374174,-0.009170387,-0.026948176,0.008945193,0.01693957,0.032477934,0.04311208,-0.011722582,0.009070301,-0.009652051,0.010915638,0.033178534,-0.0072624963,-0.011078278,-0.021118162,0.021318335,0.0005500825,0.016689355,-0.040885165,-0.019166484,-0.028124189,-0.039634086,-0.007681607,-0.0033341176,0.005576671,-0.052895494,0.019366657,-0.01959185,-0.0041004014,0.04756591,-0.009458135,0.037282065,0.002491205,0.015763558,0.015751047,-0.012986169,-0.021643614,0.047215607,0.0056517357,0.014212224,0.059150875,0.0632544,-0.050293256,0.01349911,-0.0072374744,0.03192746,-0.032553,0.047165565,-0.017715236,0.04366255,-0.0787177,-0.00815076,-0.011353515,-0.0133114485,-0.0009351793,0.030351104,0.026748005,0.005955122,0.03352884,0.018240688,-0.03470485,0.036431335,-0.030000802,-0.0122292675,-0.03868327,0.03555558,-0.04786617,-0.015625939,0.047766082,-0.04861681,-0.009207919,0.006055208,0.040234603,0.003965911,-0.013962008,0.019691937,-0.024108235,0.015425767,-0.027798908,0.006530617,-0.036256183,-0.010552826,-0.062453713,-0.00791