196	12. CUIDADOS COM AS PECAS\nDurar mais: Guardar individualmente e evitar contato com quimicos.\nBanho com peca: Nao recomendamos. O cloro e sais da agua desgastam o brilho.\nPerfume: Passe o perfume, espere secar por 5 minutos e so entao coloque a semijoia.\nLimpeza: Apenas flanela seca ou agua morna e sabao neutro.\nOnde guardar? Em locais secos, longe do sol e da umidade (evite o banheiro).\nProtetor solar: Estraga sim. Ele contem quimicos que atacam o banho.	[0.060477618,0.038473777,0.023145756,0.042821843,0.002956354,0.01082075,0.0074993125,-0.027845178,0.00828438,-0.039264336,0.02185012,-0.011979136,-0.03329124,-0.04607191,0.013845729,0.033071637,-0.0024004937,-0.025385667,0.019851767,0.014098268,-0.0019173755,0.042602245,-0.04135053,-0.02144386,0.052572045,-0.012714793,0.01625034,0.009914904,0.054241,0.0090365065,0.05151797,-0.007164424,0.034982152,0.017205596,0.028657695,0.04071369,-0.02714246,-0.03520175,-0.0045072734,-0.01367005,0.0031896783,0.039198454,-0.04365632,-0.01883063,0.05160581,0.04029645,0.006840515,0.0092780655,0.03838594,0.049673337,0.044886075,0.050639573,-0.039659616,0.019983526,0.014987645,-0.062102653,-0.0052758707,0.008630249,-0.031007405,0.023387315,0.008783968,0.007427943,-0.05485588,0.025758985,-0.058018107,0.01640406,0.0078012613,0.01341751,-0.035245672,-0.052528128,0.0015673892,0.00088869047,0.03586055,0.0037798511,-0.056568753,-0.017897334,-0.0074828425,-0.022882236,0.041723847,0.041745808,-0.033730436,-0.0060719177,-0.04594015,0.04923414,-0.034718633,0.028438095,-0.055338997,-0.012670874,-0.018731812,0.031424645,-0.042536363,-0.02165248,-0.009651384,-0.016865218,-0.037090305,0.012550094,-0.022344219,-0.010387042,-0.025166068,0.0050562713,-0.014515507,-0.021224262,-0.031556405,-0.00021050642,0.010573701,-0.01369201,-0.0602141,0.0049931365,-0.040098812,-0.01896239,0.05191325,-0.0050068614,-0.036299746,0.07892395,-0.011276418,0.071325816,-0.017227557,0.034147676,0.024375511,-0.042821843,-0.02984353,0.0013896511,0.016151521,-0.030019